Why KVM?

	KVM lets you split a single machine into multiple different VMs each running a different OS (even Windows)
	
How do I configure KVM virtualization?

	virsh on the CLI
	
	Or via the admin console
	
How popular is KVM?

	Very! RHEL is often used as a thich host deploying multiple other VMs
	
	There is even a type of RHEL for this:
		Red Hat Virtualization Hypervisor
		
		Then, of course, Red Hat OpenShift Virtualization to enable deployment and containers on bare metal
		

